title: Des Duguid
text: Des Duguid (6 November 1941 – 16 May 2008) was an Australian <a href="boxing">boxer</a>. He competed in the <a href="Boxing%20at%20the%201960%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Welterweight">men's welterweight</a> event at the <a href="1960%20Summer%20Olympics">1960 Summer Olympics</a>.
